'''Colvale Igorz'''
[[File:Church of St.Francis de Assis in Goa - DSC 0927.jpg|thumbnail|St.Francis de Assis-chi Igroz]]
==Sthapna==
St.Francis de Asssi-chi igroz Bardez talukachea Colvale gavant asa. Chapora noichea dokshinik hi igroz asa.

==Itihas==
===Poile Bandop===
St.Francis de Assis-achi igroz 1591 vorsa bandhli. Colvale ani Camurlimchi Communidadin hea igorjek bandhpak khub adhar kelo. Hi igroz Bardez Talukeachi poili 24 igrozan modli ek. Jen'na Afonso de Albuquerque Goian ail'lo, thani Bardezcho taluka Franciscanank dhekrik korpak dil'lo. Hea khatir thani 24 igroz bhandleo.

===Bhettovan===
St.Francis de Assi-achi igroz St.Francis-chea ghayank orpit kel'li. Tachea hathink, payank ani kuchiex, Christahe ghaye zale. Ho sant, Franciscan missionaricho sonsthapok aslo.

===Punarbandhanni===
1638 vorosan Sambhajin Bardez talukacho akromon kelo. Thane St.Francis de Assis-chi igrozechem tin altar lasoile ani padri ravtelea bhaganthui uzo lailo. Theach vorsa tho gelea upranth, igrozachi altaran and padrikaranche ghor porthun bhandlem.

==Vastushastra==

===Shoili=== 
[[File:Monument of Christ the King and grotto of Our Lady, with Piazza Cross in the distance - DSC 0925.JPG|thumbnail|right|Saibin Maichi image, Christ Raicho image ani mukhar 'Piazza' khuris]]
Hi igroz 'Mannerist, Neo-Roman' fetin bandla. Saibin Mai-chi and Christ Rai-cho image igorchehi fuldleant bandhlele asa, ani mache mukhar, ek voldlo khuris 'Piazza' fetin ubo kela. [[File:Sit-out behind the church of St.Francis of Assisi, Goa-india - DSC 0921.JPG|thumbnail|right|Igorche fatleant bospacho zago]]

Igorche bithor panch altaram asa. Mukaari dhara voir, dhon angebodve ani sant rakhno dovortha.

Fatleant ek bospacho zago madlili asa. Adle tempan lok noi par korun fatleant-san, xezarea gavantsan ietalim. 1971 vorosan, thea fatlea suvathicher ek bospacho zagea bandlolo. Maghir, 2008 vorosan, Mr.Wendell Rodrigues hi zago poroth aning borem baxin bandlo.

